  "description": "A two-chamber refrigerator in the BlackSteel color (dark stainless steel) has expanded the iQ300 line of the Siemens brand in 2022. Although the series combines standard-class models, the unit can be attributed to advanced solutions. The corresponding status is confirmed by visual external touch control, as well as the presence of two cooling circuits, thanks to which it is possible to independently regulate the temperature regimes in two compartments. Also, the chips of the device include the Full No Frost system, which contributes to both a more even distribution of cold inside, and simple maintenance (no manual defrosting is required). With dimensions of 203x70x67 cm, the Siemens KG49NXXEA refrigerator holds 438 liters, which can satisfy the needs of even large families. The freezer for 108 liters is located below, it is divided into 3 drawers and is characterized by good performance (up to 12 kg per day). And when there is a power outage, spoilage of products in the freezer does not threaten within 16 hours. The 330-litre fridge compartment has freshness (for meat and fish) and humidity (for fruits and vegetables) zones, as well as 4 open shelves and door pockets, a hanging bottle holder. Among other chips, it is worth highlighting the door closing indicator, moderate noise (class C - up to 40 dB) and energy consumption E (similar to A + according to the usual marking).",
